replies.body:
Broporo ooooon duty! {{summoner:31}} 

When you mentioned that it takes 3 or more seconds before your champion reacts to your commands, it really sounds like you might be experiencing some packet loss. Essentially what's happening is when you use an ability, that command has to goto our servers and then come back to each player. If some of that data gets lost along the away, some funky stuff like rubberbanding or those delays can happen. 

Let's use our [**log reader**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/209765743) to check for any packet loss. Take your recent game logs that had problems, pop it into that log reader, then use something like Gyazo to link me a screenshot here to look over!
